All Classes

Class Description
ClassSchedule
The Schedule class manages all the fitness classes at the gym.
Constants
The Constants class contains a list of public constants that can be used across other classes
Date
The Date class represents a calendar date consisting of year, month, and day
Family
The family class represents a member who has a family plan.
FitnessClass
The FitnessClass class represents the fitness classes at the gym.
GymManagerController
The GymManagerController class is the class that processes the user interactions
GymManagerMain
The GymManagerMain class sets up and launches the application
Location
The Location enum defines the locations of the gym.
Member
The Member class represents a member of the gym and is comparable based on name.
MemberDatabase
The MemberDatabase class contains a list of all the members of the gym, stored in an array of Member objects.
Month
The Month enum consists of all the months and their corresponding integer value
Plan
The plans class includes the various subscription plans to the gym
Premium
The premium class represents a member with a premium membership Each premium object contains fields including the first name, last name, date of birth, and location of the member.
Time
The Time enum represents the two times at which fitness classes are offered.
